text: i would recommend this company . I am very satisfied with the company . Michelle the rep for my area is very helpful and Chris calls every week to change our mat . We enjoy seeing Chris come to change the mat as he always has a smile and very good at his job. He gives his job 100% which is very rare nowadays .
